modName: Whisper Level 81 MAX STATS AND PERKS and Level 1 Def
summary: A level 81 redguard female with all stats maxed and all perks unlocked.
descriptionHtml:
I have provided my current save for her as well as a save back in Helgen\'s Keep with Hadvar.
Savegame 11 is my current save that is already into the main story and Savegame 12 is the save for starting in Helgen\'s Keep.

*************************************************************************
*************************************************************************
                            SPOILERS!!!!!!!
*************************************************************************
*************************************************************************
With the level 81 file I had just found Esbern and returned to Delphine. I have HEAVILY enchanted equipment as well. My original intent was for an assassin type character but since all stats are maxed and all perks are unlocked, you can play as her however you wish. The outfit I\'m wearing in the screenshots is the Triss Dark Brotherhood armor replacer. Actually it\'s from the stand alone .esp and I\'m wearing the \"Wonderous Armor\" I crafted so I could enchant it. My weapons are an enchanted Daedric bow and an enchanted Daedric Katana. There are also other mods I used that I will list now.

Beautiful Hair Retexture by Bloodysunday: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5152 (Wooly style)

Detailed Faces v2 by Xenius: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26&navtag=file/images.php?id=26&tab=3

Colorful Dragons 3 HD by Luddemann: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3740

No Helmet Mod by vuradic: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=562

Pretty Eyes by pikkatze: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3424

Triss Armor Retextured by Psyke23: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4708

Weapons of the Third Era by 747823: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3871

Tytanis - The Ultimate Mod - Crafts - Spells - Items - MORE by Tytanis: http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1601
_________________________________________________________________________________________
All that\'s really required is the hair pack and eye pack. The rest is only if you want some of the weapons I have or the armor I\'m wearing and is not at all necessary.
author: TKHawke
